{"tid":1983383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國（支那大不利顛省）係垃圾，不服來辯","createTime":"2020-04-21T19:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T03:27:32.000Z","uid":36775,"like":25,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0d273ede8087ece218102d2c3adf3b5fd785881c","tid":1983383,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T19:30:58.000Z","msg":"LONDON (Reuters) - Britain&rsquo;s government made a firm decision to allow China&rsquo;s Huawei to have a role in building the country&rsquo;s 5G phone network and as far as the foreign ministry&rsquo;s top official understands it is not being reopened, he said on Tuesday.<br />\n<br />\nBritain decided in January to allow Huawei into what the government said were non-sensitive parts of its 5G network, capping its involvement at 35%.<br />\n<br />\nAsked whether he would advise the foreign minister to try to change the government&rsquo;s position on Huawei, Simon McDonald, permanent under secretary and head of the diplomatic service at the foreign ministry, told lawmakers: &ldquo;As you know ... the government decided to proceed with an investment but with very strict conditions ... As far as I know that ... is a firm decision and is not being reopened.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;China is a very important partner of the United Kingdom and I think it&rsquo;s compatible to proceed with the Huawei decision and have the strategically independent relationship that I have been talking about.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-britain-huawei-idUSKCN22327E?utm_campaign=trueAnthem%3A+Trending+Content&amp;utm_medium=trueAnthem&amp;utm_source=facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-health-coronavirus-britain-huawei-idUSKCN22327E%3Futm_campaign%3DtrueAnthem%253A%2BTrending%2BContent%26utm_medium%3DtrueAnthem%26utm_source%3Dfacebook&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8hPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=ec3995de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-health-coronavirus-britain-huawei-idUSKCN22327E%3Futm_campaign%3DtrueAnthem%253A%2BTrending%2BContent%26utm_medium%3DtrueAnthem%26utm_source%3Dfacebook&h=2125cf43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-britain-huawei-idUSKCN22327E?utm_campaign=trueAnthem%3A+Trending+Content&amp;utm_medium=trueAnthem&amp;utm_source=facebook</a><br />\n<br />\n信英國班傻仔天真過天真嬌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個首相接近死都可以繼續奶共<br />\n歸英班傻仔仲可以對日落國有希望<br />\n用Bno入保守黨投票都可以打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要比bno一早比撚咗<br />\n除非你係政治難民、移民過去<br />\nBNO平權去到你死戈日都平唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎bin我屍，我都好希望你bin到<br />\nBin到先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc3e8f0101f3b47b2628bbc43eadc4ae92c9d7f","tid":1983383,"uid":36775,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T19:32:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾英國<br />\n等比支那控制曬啲情報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868a7ecd64a56e198766ba67ae9ac00c1ec578bc","tid":1983383,"uid":63669,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T19:32:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾建造左呢個中國城市，而住係由垃圾建造既你係垃圾中既垃"},{"pid":"d1f70563b38a6f0c531a0f5ed5d42fe14fc3f961","tid":1983383,"uid":36775,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"868a7ecd64a56e198766ba67ae9ac00c1ec578bc","tid":1983383,"uid":63669,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T19:32:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾建造左呢個中國城市，而住係由垃圾建造既你係垃圾中既垃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20